quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  2,120,"Yahuud e nasaara en mbeletaake ma haa njokkaa laawol ma…ì…ìe , wi' …ìe nganndee ko peewal Alla woni peewal so a jokkii belee…óe ma…ì…ìe …ìaawo nde ke…ì…óaa ganndal ,ndeen woodantaa ma to Allah keedo wonaa ballo ne ."
  2,121,"∆Åeen …ìe min ngaddani deftere ndee e…ìe nde njannga no haaniri ko …ìeen tigi ngoong…óini nde, kala mbo yeddi nde ko …ìeen tigi ngoni bonnoraa…ìe."
  2,122,"Onon …ìi…ì…ìe Isra'iil ciftoree mo∆¥∆¥ereeji am …ói mi wa…óanii on, Miin tigi wa…ói on …ìur…ìe he winndere ndee."
  2,123,"Kulee √±ande fittaandu alaa ko waawani fittaandu wo…óndu te ndu ja…ìantaake coodtiigu kadi tefaneede nafataa ndu, …ìe ke…ìataa ballo."
  2,124,"Nde Alla humpitori Ibrahiima konngi o timmini …ói, o wi'i: Miin Mi wa…óat ma gardotoo…óo yim…ìe …ìe, Ibarahiima wi'i wa…ó …óum kadi he …ìesngu am o wi'i too√±oo…ìe …ìee ke…ìataa fodoore am."
  2,125,"Nde min mba…ói suudu nduu ruttorde yim…ìe e hoolaare , njokito-…óee darnde Ibrahiima wona juulirde, min ngaadanii Ibrahiima e Ismaa'iila yo …ìe la…ì…ìin suudu am nduu ngam wanngotoo…ìe e ufnotoo…ìe e juuloo…ìe."
  2,126,"Nde Ibrahiima wi'i joom am wa…óan min nduu suudu leydi hoolniindi nje…óaa yim…ìe mayru …ìi…ì…ìe le…ó…óe wonande goong…óin…ìe Alla e √±ande wattan O wi'i kala jeddu…óo mi weltina mo see…óa fawoo heen mi fa'na mon lette jayngol e battane bon…óe."